wikibase-rescore-profile-prefix: Default rescore profile for completion search. (See [https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/search-request-rescore.html Rescoring] in the Elastic documentation for explanation.)
wikibase-rescore-profile-prefix-boost:
"Rescore" is not a verb. So translate as "profile of rescore" and not as "to rescore a profile".
:''([https://www.mediawiki.org/w/index.php?title=Extension:CirrusSearch/Profiles#Wikibase Reference] states: "Added '''rescore profiles''' that are used for Wikibase entities")''

"Completion search" referred [[MediaWiki:Wikibaselexeme-rescore-profile-prefix/en|here]] as "Prefix (completion) search" is a search to find possible completions for the existing typed characters (the "prefix", one guesses).
:''([https://www.mediawiki.org/w/index.php?title=Extension:CirrusSearch/Profiles#Context Reference] states: "a '''rescore profile''' can be applied to regular search, '''prefix search''', Wikibase search, etc.")''

Apparently related:
* [[MediaWiki:Wikibaselexeme-rescore-profile-prefix/en]]
wikibase-rescore-profile-fulltext: Default rescore profile for fulltext search. (See [https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/search-request-rescore.html Rescoring] in the Elastic documentation for explanation.)
wikibase-rescore-profile-fulltext-phrase: Default rescore profile for fulltext search with phrase rescoring. (See [https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/search-request-rescore.html Rescoring] in the Elastic documentation for explanation.)
wikibase-search-bad-entity-type: Error message displayed when user supplies bad entity type to wbsearchentities
wikibase-search-bad-profile-name: Error message displayed when user supplies bad search profile name
wikibase-search-namespace-mix: Warning when using mixed namespaces in fulltext search
wikibase-search-config-notfound: Error message displayed when configured search profile can not be loaded
wikibase-search-config-badclass: Error message displayed when configured query builder can not be found or has wrong type
wikibase-haswbstatement-feature-no-valid: Error message when haswbstatement keyword has no valid arguments
wikibaescirrussearch-inlabel-unknown-lan:
Error message when an unknown language code is provided to the inlabel search keyword.

Parameters:
* $1 - The unknown language code.
wikibasecirrussearch-inlabel-too-many-la:
Error message displayed when inlabel keyword was provided more than the system limited number of languages.

Parameters:
* $1 - The number of languages allowed.
* $2 - The number of languages provided.
wikibasecirrussearch-inlabel-no-query-pr: Error message displayed when inlabel keyword was provided an empty string to search for
